dc_title_s: Nevada Joint Union High School District, Nevada County, California, 2020
dc_description_s: This layer delineates the Nevada Joint High School District. The District is divided into the five Board of Trustee Areas. Most Trustee boundaries follow Road Centerlines. Nevada County (Calif.). Geographic Information Services. (2020). Nevada Joint Union High School District, Nevada County, California, 2020. Nevada County (Calif.). Geographic Information Services. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/jt905zc2019 This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
